-- Architecture:
--   1. SCAN ONCE on startup → creates Drawing objects for every crystal immediately
--   2. ChildAdded / ChildRemoved → reactively adds/removes crystals, no polling
--   3. Heartbeat → only WorldToScreen + set position/visible on existing Drawings (zero allocation)
--   4. UI loop → fully independent task.spawn, owns its thread completely
-- ======================================================================

